msgid "Generate screenshot thumbnails"
msgstr "Générer les miniatures de captures"

#: ../../command-line-interface.rst:164 5020be3c978c4aa99ff53ee00985c4a3
msgid ""
"Pre-generates the JPEG thumbnails served on group/market detail pages. On"
" first run this can take a while (hundreds of thousands of screenshots); "
"subsequent runs are incremental and only touch screenshots that are newer"
" than their thumbnail."
msgstr ""
"Pré-génère les miniatures JPEG servies sur les pages de détail de "
"groupes/marchés. Le premier run peut être long (centaines de milliers de "
"captures) ; les runs suivants sont incrémentaux et ne touchent que les "
"captures plus récentes que leur miniature."

#: ../../command-line-interface.rst:175 a0c798d39ea449e9b5b93e44dfe168b0
msgid ""
"The script skips ``source/screenshots/old`` and "
"``source/screenshots/logo``, and mirrors the source directory tree under "
"``source/screenshots/thumbs/``."
msgstr ""
"Le script ignore ``source/screenshots/old`` et "
"``source/screenshots/logo``, et reproduit l'arborescence source sous "
"``source/screenshots/thumbs/``."

#: ../../command-line-interface.rst:179 0e991259a2894bbfb4f3809767e99d98
